        <paragraph nr="2">
          <sen nr="1">Landhelgin skal auk þess afmörkuð af línu sem alls staðar er 12 sjómílur frá stórstraumsfjöruborði Kolbeinseyjar (67°08'59,57"N, 18°40'58,70"V), Hvalbaks (64°35'45,42"N, 13°16'37,71"V) og ystu annesjum og skerjum Grímseyjar (66°34'03,27"N, 18°01'18,74"V; 66°33'33,72"N, 18°00'03,65"V; 66°32'45,09"N, 17°58'38,74"V; 66°32'00,88"N, 17°58'40,37"V; 66°31'29,42"N, 17°58'45,61"V; 66°31'36,26"N, 17°59'24,84"V; 66°31'40,69"N, 17°59'43,81"V; 66°32'15,60"N, 18°01'17,25"V; 66°32'21,61"N, 18°01'22,93"V; 66°32'33,57"N, 18°01'34,45"V; 66°33'04,77"N, 18°01'48,60"V; 66°34'01,34"N, 18°01'28,13"V).</sen>
        </paragraph>
      </subart>
      <subart nr="2">
        <paragraph nr="1">
          <sen nr="1">Hver sjómíla reiknast 1.852 metrar.</sen>
        </paragraph>
      </subart>
      <subart nr="3">
        <paragraph nr="1">
          <sen nr="1">Innsævi er hafsvæði landmegin við grunnlínur.</sen>
        </paragraph>
